            <title>[KAFKA-14035] QuorumController handleRenounce throws NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-14035</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes when the controller is rolled you can encounter the following exception, after which the controller in-memory state seems to become inconsistent with the Metadata Log.&lt;/p&gt;

